Queries

api

Response

Returns an Api

Arguments
Name Description
id - StringExpression
name - StringExpression
description - StringExpression
type - ApiTypeExpression
role - RoleExpression
realm - RealmExpression
includeDeprecated - Boolean Default = false
version - IntExpression
realmId - IntExpression
createUserId - StringExpression
createTime - StringExpression
updateUserId - StringExpression
updateTime - StringExpression
createGroupId - StringExpression
roleId - IntExpression
cond - Conditional Default = AND
exs - [ApiExpression]

Example

Query
query api(
  $id: StringExpression,
  $name: StringExpression,
  $description: StringExpression,
  $type: ApiTypeExpression,
  $role: RoleExpression,
  $realm: RealmExpression,
  $includeDeprecated: Boolean,
  $version: IntExpression,
  $realmId: IntExpression,
  $createUserId: StringExpression,
  $createTime: StringExpression,
  $updateUserId: StringExpression,
  $updateTime: StringExpression,
  $createGroupId: StringExpression,
  $roleId: IntExpression,
  $cond: Conditional,
  $exs: [ApiExpression]
) {
  api(
    id: $id,
    name: $name,
    description: $description,
    type: $type,
    role: $role,
    realm: $realm,
    includeDeprecated: $includeDeprecated,
    version: $version,
    realmId: $realmId,
    createUserId: $createUserId,
    createTime: $createTime,
    updateUserId: $updateUserId,
    updateTime: $updateTime,
    createGroupId: $createGroupId,
    roleId: $roleId,
    cond: $cond,
    exs: $exs
  ) {
    id
    name
    description
    type
    role {
      ...RoleFragment
    }
    realm {
      ...RealmFragment
    }
    isDeprecated
    version
    realmId
    createUserId
    createTime
    updateUserId
    updateTime
    createGroupId
    idCount
    idMax
    idMin
    nameCount
    nameMax
    nameMin
    descriptionCount
    descriptionMax
    descriptionMin
    roleId
    roleIdCount
    roleIdSum
    roleIdAvg
    roleIdMax
    roleIdMin
    realmIdCount
    realmIdSum
    realmIdAvg
    realmIdMax
    realmIdMin
  }
}
Variables

  "description": StringExpression,

  "version": IntExpression,
  "realmId": IntExpression,
  "createUserId": StringExpression,
  "createTime": StringExpression,
  "updateUserId": StringExpression,
  "updateTime": StringExpression,
  "createGroupId": StringExpression,
  "roleId": IntExpression,
  "cond": "AND",
  "exs": [ApiExpression]
}

Queries

apiConnection

Response

Returns an ApiConnection

Arguments
Name Description
id - StringExpression
name - StringExpression
description - StringExpression
type - ApiTypeExpression
role - RoleExpression
realm - RealmExpression
includeDeprecated - Boolean Default = false
version - IntExpression
realmId - IntExpression
createUserId - StringExpression
createTime - StringExpression
updateUserId - StringExpression
updateTime - StringExpression
createGroupId - StringExpression
roleId - IntExpression
orderBy - ApiOrderBy
groupBy - [String!]
cond - Conditional Default = AND
exs - [ApiExpression]
first - Int
last - Int
offset - Int
after - ID
before - ID

Example

Query
query apiConnection(
  $id: StringExpression,
  $name: StringExpression,
  $description: StringExpression,
  $type: ApiTypeExpression,
  $role: RoleExpression,
  $realm: RealmExpression,
  $includeDeprecated: Boolean,
  $version: IntExpression,
  $realmId: IntExpression,
  $createUserId: StringExpression,
  $createTime: StringExpression,
  $updateUserId: StringExpression,
  $updateTime: StringExpression,
  $createGroupId: StringExpression,
  $roleId: IntExpression,
  $orderBy: ApiOrderBy,
  $groupBy: [String!],
  $cond: Conditional,
  $exs: [ApiExpression],
  $first: Int,
  $last: Int,
  $offset: Int,
  $after: ID,
  $before: ID
) {
  apiConnection(
    id: $id,
    name: $name,
    description: $description,
    type: $type,
    role: $role,
    realm: $realm,
    includeDeprecated: $includeDeprecated,
    version: $version,
    realmId: $realmId,
    createUserId: $createUserId,
    createTime: $createTime,
    updateUserId: $updateUserId,
    updateTime: $updateTime,
    createGroupId: $createGroupId,
    roleId: $roleId,
    orderBy: $orderBy,
    groupBy: $groupBy,
    cond: $cond,
    exs: $exs,
    first: $first,
    last: $last,
    offset: $offset,
    after: $after,
    before: $before
  ) {
    totalCount
    pageInfo {
      ...PageInfoFragment
    }
    edges {
      ...ApiEdgeFragment
    }
  }
}
Variables
{
  "id": StringExpression,
  "name": StringExpression,
  "description": StringExpression,
  "type": ApiTypeExpression,
  "role": RoleExpression,
  "realm": RealmExpression,
  "includeDeprecated": false,
  "version": IntExpression,
  "realmId": IntExpression,
  "createUserId": StringExpression,
  "createTime": StringExpression,
  "updateUserId": StringExpression,
  "updateTime": StringExpression,
  "createGroupId": StringExpression,
  "roleId": IntExpression,
  "orderBy": ApiOrderBy,
  "groupBy": ["xyz789"],
  "cond": "AND",
  "exs": [ApiExpression],
  "first": 123,
  "last": 987,
  "offset": 987,
  "after": 4,
  "before": 4
}
Response
{
  "data": {
    "apiConnection": {
      "totalCount": 123,
      "pageInfo": PageInfo,
      "edges": [ApiEdge]
    }
  }
}

Query
query group(
  $id: StringExpression,
  $name: StringExpression,
  $parent: GroupExpression,
  $subGroups: GroupExpression,
  $users: UserExpression,
  $roles: RoleExpression,
  $realm: RealmExpression,
  $includeDeprecated: Boolean,
  $version: IntExpression,
  $realmId: IntExpression,
  $createUserId: StringExpression,
  $createTime: StringExpression,
  $updateUserId: StringExpression,
  $updateTime: StringExpression,
  $createGroupId: StringExpression,
  $parentId: IntExpression,
  $userGroup: UserGroupExpression,
  $groupRole: GroupRoleExpression,
  $cond: Conditional,
  $exs: [GroupExpression]
) {
  group(
    id: $id,
    name: $name,
    parent: $parent,
    subGroups: $subGroups,
    users: $users,
    roles: $roles,
    realm: $realm,

    createTime: $createTime,
    updateUserId: $updateUserId,
    updateTime: $updateTime,

    groupRole: $groupRole,
    cond: $cond,
    exs: $exs

Example

Query
query groupConnection(
  $id: StringExpression,
  $name: StringExpression,
  $parent: GroupExpression,
  $subGroups: GroupExpression,
  $users: UserExpression,
  $roles: RoleExpression,
  $realm: RealmExpression,
  $includeDeprecated: Boolean,
  $version: IntExpression,
  $realmId: IntExpression,
  $createUserId: StringExpression,
  $createTime: StringExpression,
  $updateUserId: StringExpression,
  $updateTime: StringExpression,
  $createGroupId: StringExpression,
  $parentId: IntExpression,
  $userGroup: UserGroupExpression,
  $groupRole: GroupRoleExpression,
  $orderBy: GroupOrderBy,
  $groupBy: [String!],
  $cond: Conditional,
  $exs: [GroupExpression],
  $first: Int,
  $last: Int,
  $offset: Int,
  $after: ID,
  $before: ID
) {
  groupConnection(
    id: $id,
    name: $name,
    parent: $parent,
    subGroups: $subGroups,
    users: $users,
    roles: $roles,
    realm: $realm,

  $before: ID
) {

    orderBy: $orderBy,
    groupBy: $groupBy,
    cond: $cond,
    exs: $exs,
    first: $first,
    last: $last,
    offset: $offset,
    after: $after,
    before: $before
  ) {
    id

    isDeprecated
    version

    createUserId
    createTime

    updateTime
    createGroupId
    idCount
